-- 
Spain Businesses Support Early Elections, El Pais Poll Shows

-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 
2011-07-24T11:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-24/spain-businesses-support-early-elections-el-pais-poll-shows.html
A poll of 232 companies showed that
67.5 percent favor early general elections in  Spain  compared
with 18.9 percent that don’t,  El Pais  reported, citing the
survey.  As many as 62.6 percent of the companies said that a change
of government would help to restore confidence compared with
18.2 percent that said it wouldn’t, the Madrid-based newspaper
reported. The poll was carried out by Deloitte LLP this month,
El Pais said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Charles Penty in Madrid at 
 cpenty@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
